name: PythonNet3 Engine
description:
An engine for Dynamo's Python nodes based on version 3 of the Python.NET open source library. This engine behaves similarly to the default "CPython3" engine, with some improvements:
- Fixed overloaded method resolution.  ​
- Improved generic method inference (don’t need to specify generics as often).  
- Define Python classes inheriting from .NET classes and interfaces.​
- Better extension method support, including Linq.  ​
- Override .Net methods that have an `out` or `ref`. 
 
Please see our blog post for more detail: https://dynamobim.org/pythonnet3-a-new-dynamo-python-to-fix-everything
